%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: d6fced335fe0e624e8c9d175d9ff6239, type: 3}
  m_Name: ForestKing_FirstMeeting
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  startNodeIndex: 0
  nodes:
  - editorLabel: King - Introduction
    lines:
    - speaker: ???
      text: ...You.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 1
      tags: []
    - speaker: ???
      text: A human. In my sanctuary. How unusual.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: I am the one they call the King of this forest. Or I was, before that
        creature took root in the western caves.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: I tried to drive it out. As is my duty. As I have done for every threat
        that has ever encroached upon these woods.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: I failed.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: The wound it left me... I can barely stand, let alone fight. And without
        my presence keeping order, the lesser creatures have gone feral.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: "That is why your kind has been troubled. The monsters harassing the
        village, the chaos in the woods \u2014 it all stems from my failure."
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices:
    - choiceText: (What is this creature?)
      nextNodeIndex: 1
    - choiceText: (What do you want from me?)
      nextNodeIndex: 2
    - choiceText: (...)
      nextNodeIndex: 3
    nextNodeIndex: -1
  - editorLabel: King - About the Wraith
    lines:
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: "A Wraith. An old one. It feeds on the life force of anything nearby
        \u2014 plants, animals, even the land itself."
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: It has nested deep in the caves to the west, past the great tree. You
        will know you are close when the air suddenly grows cold and heavy with it's
        stench.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: It is not especially strong in body. But it is cunning. It drains your
        stamina, silences your abilities, and makes you slow while it strikes again
        and again.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: I was faster than it. Stronger. But I was not prepared for its tricks.
        Do not make my mistake.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 4
  - editorLabel: King - Request
    lines:
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: I cannot ask anything of you. You owe me nothing, and I owe you even
        less.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: But if you care for the village, that creature must die. It will only
        grow stronger the longer it feeds.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: The cave is to the west, past the great tree. The flowers on its trunk
        still bloom, that tree is the last thing in this forest resisting the Wraith's
        influence.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: When those flowers wilt, this forest is lost. And then, your village
        will be next.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 4
  - editorLabel: King - Silent Response
    lines:
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: You say nothing. Good. I am tired of words.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: If you wish to act, go west past the great tree. The cave there holds
        the source of everything wrong with this forest.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: If you wish to leave... I will not stop you. I cannot stop much of anything
        right now.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 4
  - editorLabel: King - Farewell
    lines:
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: One more thing.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: The creatures in this forest... they are not evil. They are frightened,
        confused. My presence once kept them calm.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: If you can end the Wraith, the forest will heal.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: King of the Forest
      text: I will be here. Waiting. It is all I can do.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: -1
